data.description: Welcome to your dream home just minutes away from town in a peaceful county setting. This charming brick home, adorned with a sleek metal roof, is nestled on a spacious .78-acre lot. The property boasts convenience with community water and a private septic system.  As you approach, you'll notice a small outbuilding perfect for additional storage, a fenced backyard providing privacy, and a delightful covered deck off the dining area – an ideal spot for outdoor gatherings or quiet relaxation. The two-car garage not only provides shelter for your vehicles but also features utility storage for added convenience.  Step inside to discover an updated kitchen that exudes modern elegance. The kitchen boasts newer countertops, stainless steel appliances, and freshly painted cabinets. The dining and kitchen combo offers ample space for both bar seating and a table, making it a versatile and inviting area.  The dining area is enhanced by a cathedral ceiling, creating an open and airy atmosphere. The generously sized living room features a vaulted ceiling, providing a sense of grandeur and comfort. New luxury vinyl plank (LVP) floors grace all rooms, adding a touch of sophistication, while the bathroom is adorned with tasteful tile flooring.  The second bathroom is thoughtfully designed with newer toilets and a walk-in shower. The master bathroom is a sanctuary with double sinks, a separate shower, and a luxurious jacuzzi tub. The master bedroom itself is a haven, featuring a vaulted ceiling and double closets, providing ample storage and creating a retreat-like ambiance.  This home seamlessly combines modern upgrades with practical features, offering comfort and style. Don't miss the opportunity to make this exquisite property your own – a perfect blend of rural tranquility and contemporary living.
